{"tid":467752,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求台北五日遊美食推介","createTime":"2017-11-13T18:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T16:17:43.000Z","uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a39d141bf1bc663d0f1ef429c3ed8d181a3c926a","tid":467752,"uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:58:21.000Z","msg":"人在台北，請問有咩係必食推介？<br />\n岩岩食左程味珍滷肉飯，覺得都有80分<br />\n黎緊會去士林，饒河同基隆夜市"},{"pid":"3ef51120acf666db402cf037be3a8b685506b015","tid":467752,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"我講既唔關野食事<br />\n係士林食完野<br />\n可以坐的士上去文化大學情人坡睇夜景<br />\n個到仲有腸仔賣<br />\n捷運市林夜市出口出去左邊有泥鯭的上去<br />\n當然都可以自己一個人坐 不過就300-400台幣"},{"pid":"a108dd492f98c9ff336c0c31591c0e09e6ccd7fb","tid":467752,"uid":69977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"台北車站地下街到有好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果巴打會去埋九份可以食芋圓"},{"pid":"92ea5cdde13af54d78b822242e8bf73b3b88b46c","tid":467752,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:24:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台北車站地下街到有好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果巴打會去埋九份可以食芋圓</blockquote><br />\n九份魚蛋湯都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272bd8ac10382ef24900e836da38f3b3114e33a6","tid":467752,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台北車站地下街到有好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果巴打會去埋九份可以食芋圓</blockquote><br />\n地下街冇咩好食渣wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係多電玩野<br />\n反而北車微風breeze有唔少好野食"},{"pid":"d76c034d5c8aa70fcb742dd3342fa5fbf008a19b","tid":467752,"uid":17170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:29:30.000Z","msg":"程味珍都值80分？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試